title: The Psychology of Russian Doll
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda and Humberto analyze the psychology of the Netflix show Russian Doll. They talk about existential fears, regrets, and women in control of art.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

Feb 24, 2019.

Email: Contact@PsychologyInSeattle.com
